## Limitations

The report is based on available online sources, which may not cover all aspects of IoT's impact comprehensively. Some sources lacked publication dates, which could affect the currency of the information. Additionally, the focus was primarily on consumer applications, potentially overlooking industrial and commercial impacts of IoT.

